(271, 1, '2015-01-26 16:50:19', '2015-01-26 16:50:19', 'The Arc Lamps are five individual chandeliers constructed out of recycled oversized light bulbs and custom LED lights. Constructed in 2013 and debuted at the <a href="http://www.biennialoftheamericas.org/">Biennale of the Americas</a> in Denver, they make an impact both near and far. The design was based off of The Edison Chandelier, using a similar construction but pushing the boundaries of scale by incorporating bulbs still being used in commercial lighting. The Arc Lamps currently hang in <a href="http://thestudioboulder.com">The Studio (Boulder)</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>Some Photography by <a href="http://www.davistilly.com/">Ashley Davis / Davis Tilly Photography</a>', 'The Arc Lamps', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '94-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-26 16:50:19', '2015-01-26 16:50:19', '', 94, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/94-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
