(632, 1, '2015-01-28 03:46:32', '2015-01-28 03:46:32', 'Created from custom hand cut thick Pyrex, The Kitchen Sconce and The Kitchen Pendant were designed and are featured in <a title="The Kitchen" href="http://thekitchen.com/" target="_blank">The Kitchen</a> restaurants nationwide. Mixing clean simple aesthetic with vintage forms, these fixtures blends function and beauty.\r\n\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>', 'The Kitchen Pendant and Sconce', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '98-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 03:46:32', '2015-01-28 03:46:32', '', 98, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/98-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(633, 1, '2015-01-28 03:48:04', '2015-01-28 03:48:04', 'The Arc Lamps are five individual chandeliers constructed out of recycled oversized light bulbs and custom LED lights. Constructed in 2013 and debuted at the <a title="Biennial of the Americas" href="http://www.biennialoftheamericas.org/">Biennale of the Americas</a> in Denver, they make an impact both near and far. The design was based off of The Edison Chandelier, using a similar construction but pushing the boundaries of scale by incorporating bulbs still being used in commercial lighting. The Arc Lamps currently hang in <a title="The Studio (Boulder)" href="http://thestudioboulder.com" target="_blank">The Studio (Boulder)</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Arc Lamps', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '94-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 03:48:04', '2015-01-28 03:48:04', '', 94, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/94-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
