(665, 1, '2015-02-03 20:29:24', '2015-02-03 20:29:24', 'The Grove consists of 12 interactive, climbable, outdoor light sculptures created from FRP with an internal, custom wireless LED system. Larger than life chairs awaken an inner child encouraging play across the sculpture. This piece is designed and ready for the right event to build!\r\n<h4>INTERACTION:</h4>\r\nAt night each of The Grove’s platforms will sense user movement and position. By climbing, sitting and playing on chairs, you will create swirls of  light.', 'The Grove', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-grove', '', '', '2015-02-28 18:15:52', '2015-02-28 18:15:52', '', 0, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/?post_type=art&#038;p=665', 0, 'art', '', 0),
