(869, 1, '2015-02-10 21:18:35', '2015-02-10 21:18:35', 'The Ms are a playful series of classic American logobilia transformed through public interaction. Whether it be in commerce, effort or time, it’s undeniable that there are symbols that have become an unrecognizable part of life. The Ms allow participants to interact with some of these symbols without cultural pressure and reminds us that their real meaning lies in playful moments. Mounted on articulating arms, participants can impact and change these pieces to be playful, traditional, ironic, or nonsensical.', 'The Ms', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-ms-7', '', '', '2015-02-10 21:18:35', '2015-02-10 21:18:35', '', 0, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/J_Lewin_M_Stills-1001_web.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0);
