(1048, 1, '2015-02-12 23:16:23', '2015-02-12 23:16:23', 'The Edison Orb is created from formed aluminum rings and customized, clear custom made incandescent bulbs. Derived in form from the original designs and molds from The Pool, it is a beautiful example of recycling beauty and function. The fixtures, handmade in Boulder, Colorado, cast a unique light pattern and transform spaces from private homes to commercial spaces. Featured in The Kitchen restaurants nationwide.', 'The Edison Orb by Jen Lewin', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-edison-orb-by-jen-lewin-17', '', '', '2015-02-12 23:16:23', '2015-02-12 23:16:23', '', 0, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/EdisonOrb3web.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
