(1189, 1, '2015-02-24 14:17:29', '2015-02-24 14:17:29', 'The Grove consists of 12 interactive, climbable, outdoor light sculptures created from FRP with an internal, custom wireless LED system. This piece is designed and ready for the right event to build!\n<h4>INTERACTION:</h4>\nAt night The Grove will glow blue. Each of The Ocean’s ice platforms will sense user movement and position. By walking over and through the ice, you will create swirls of white and blue light in your wake.\n\nDuring the day, The Ocean will reflect the existing sky. Each ice platform is created from highly resilient fiberglass, embedded LEDS and a durable reflective (mirror coating.) Viewers will experience the sensation of walking over a sea of blue glass.', 'The Grove', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '665-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-02-24 14:17:29', '2015-02-24 14:17:29', '', 665, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/665-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1191, 1, '2015-02-24 14:19:29', '2015-02-24 14:19:29', 'The Grove consists of 12 interactive, climbable, outdoor light sculptures created from FRP with an internal, custom wireless LED system. Larger than life chairs awaken an inner child encouraging play across the sculpture. This piece is designed and ready for the right event to build!\r\n<h4>INTERACTION:</h4>\r\nAt night each of The Grove’s platforms will sense user movement and position. By climbing, sitting and playing on chairs, you will create swirls of  light.', 'The Grove', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '665-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-24 14:19:29', '2015-02-24 14:19:29', '', 665, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/665-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1192, 1, '2015-02-24 14:20:59', '2015-02-24 14:20:59', 'The Leaves is a concept sketch for an interactive, climbable ground ‘form/mound” that would utilize systems of monitoring activity on and around the forms and reflect that energy in color.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4></h4>', 'The Leaves', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '671-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-24 14:20:59', '2015-02-24 14:20:59', '', 671, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/671-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1196, 1, '2015-02-24 14:28:27', '2015-02-24 14:28:27', 'The Moths are three soft interactive robotic forms that are charged to movement by human connection. The Moths are a participatory art piece; only by stopping and connecting physically do they come to life. The longer one stays, the longer the moth will continue to move even when the viewer leaves. The Moths speak to light, to community, to gathering, and have an open ethereal dream like quality that will gracefully dance and glow in space.', 'The Moths', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-24 14:28:27', '2015-02-24 14:28:27', '', 74, 'http://jenlewinstudio.com/74-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
